  <brief_title>Point of Care Ultrasonography In The Management of Undifferentiated Shock: A Pilot Randomized Controlled Trial</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Point of Care Ultrasound Guided Resuscitation and Usual Care Comparison in the Management of Undifferentiated Shock: a Pilot Study</official_title>
