  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This project aims to determine the feasibility of conducting a randomized controlled trial
      investigating point of care ultrasound guided resuscitation compared with usual care in the
      management of undifferentiated shock at the Critical Care Trauma Centre (CCTC) in London
      Health Science Centre (LHSC).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
